OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt, charity says
OL,6,FArrears on household bills have surged
OL,7,Fby 25% among those seeking debt
OL,8,Fadvice, with one charity warning this
OL,9,Fcould only worsen as many household
OL,10,Fbills are set to rise in April.
OL,12,FThe StepChange debt charity said its
OL,13,Faverage client was #3,911 in arrears
OL,14,Fon household bills, up from #3,124 in
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FOverall, the average amount of debt
OL,18,Ffor each StepChange client jumped 7%,
OL,19,Ffrom #16,706 in 2023 to #17,936 last
OL,20,Fyear.
