OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt, charity says
OL,6,FThey say those on the lowest incomes
OL,7,Fface increasing budget deficits, which
OL,8,F"could be pushing more people to rely
OL,9,Fon credit to make ends meet."
OL,11,FAs a result, they're calling on the
OL,12,Fgovernment to protect the most
OL,13,Ffinancially vulnerable households in
OL,14,Fthe Spring Statement this week.
OL,16,FMortgage arrears saw the most dramatic
OL,17,Frise, soaring by 69% from #6,054 in
OL,18,F2023 to #10,239.
