OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt, charity says
OL,6,FAlmost a fifth of StepChange clients
OL,7,F(18%) with a mortgage are now in
OL,8,Farrears, the charity said.
OL,10,FHowever, the proportion of clients
OL,11,Fwith a mortgage remained low at 14%.
OL,13,FEnergy arrears have risen by 28% year
OL,14,Fon year, with a 58% jump since 2022,
OL,15,Ffrom #1,485 to #2,340 last year.
OL,17,FCouncil tax arrears have increased by
OL,18,F14% in the last year to #1,972.
