OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt, charity says
OL,6,F"This is something which could worsen
OL,7,Fas many bills are set to rise further
OL,8,Fnext month.
OL,10,F"Consistently rising living costs are
OL,11,Fpulling higher earners into debt, with
OL,12,Fmore people finding work is not
OL,13,Fshielding them against financial
OL,14,Fhardship.
OL,16,F"Those on the lowest incomes face
OL,17,Fgrowing budget deficits and it's a
OL,18,Fconcern that this could be pushing
OL,19,Fmore people to rely on credit to make
OL,20,Fends meet.
