OL,3,CArrears on household bills surge 25%
OL,4,Camong those in debt, charity says
OL,6,F"At this week's Spring Statement, it's
OL,7,Fimportant the government does not
OL,8,Fexacerbate hardship for the most
OL,9,Ffinancially vulnerable households.
OL,11,F"This should include addressing
OL,12,Fincreasingly unaffordable household
OL,13,Fbills, such as energy and council tax,
OL,14,Fthrough targeted support aimed at
OL,15,Fdelivering long-term affordability for
OL,16,Flow income households."
